<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Questionnaire</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./styles/questionnaire.css" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('navbarLoggedIn'); -%>

        <h1 id="error" class="error"></h1>

        <h2>Please complete the following questions so we can find the right therapist for you:</h2>

        <div id="quiz-container">
            <form  id="quesForm" method="post">
                <div class="mood">
                    <h3>Over the past 2 weeks, how often have you experienced:</h3>

                    <h4>1. Little interest or pleasure in doing things?</h4>
                    <h4 id="errorQ1" class="error"></h4>
                    <div class="input-group-container">
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q1" value="0" required>Never
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q1" value="1">Rarely
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q1" value="2">Sometimes
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q1" value="3">Often
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q1" value="4">Nearly every day
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <h4>2. Difficulty falling asleep, staying asleep, or sleeping more than usual?</h4>
                    <h4 id="errorQ2" class="error"></h4>
                    <div class="input-group-container">
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q2" value="0" required>Never
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q2" value="1">Rarely
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q2" value="2">Sometimes
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q2" value="3">Often
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q2" value="4">Nearly every day
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <h4>3. Trouble focusing, anxious thoughts, or restlessness?</h4>
                    <h4 id="errorQ3" class="error"></h4>
                    <div class="input-group-container">
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q3" value="0" required>Never
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q3" value="1">Rarely
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q3" value="2">Sometimes
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q3" value="3">Often
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q3" value="4">Nearly every day
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br><br>

                <div class="family">
                    <h3>Please rate the following statements:</h3>

                    <h4>4. I am struggling to know how to parent my child, and it is interfering with my ability to
                        handle life and experience happiness.</h4>
                    <h4 id="errorQ4" class="error"></h4>
                    <div class="input-group-container">
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="0" required>Never
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="1">Rarely
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="2">Sometimes
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="3">Often
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="4">Nearly every day
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <h4>5. I am struggling in my relationship with my spouse/partner, and it is interfering with my
                        ability to handle life and experience happiness.</h4>
                    <h4 id="errorQ5" class="error"></h4>
                    <div class="input-group-container">
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q5" value="0" required>Never
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q5" value="1">Rarely
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q5" value="2">Sometimes
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q5" value="3">Often
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q5" value="4">Nearly every day
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <h4>6. I have difficulty maintaining relationships with people and find myself isolating and/or
                        pushing people away.</h4>
                    <h4 id="errorQ6" class="error"></h4>
                    <div class="input-group-container">
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q6" value="0" required>Never
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q6" value="1">Rarely
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q6" value="2">Sometimes
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q6" value="3">Often
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q6" value="4">Nearly every day
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br><br>

                <div class="addiction">
                    <h3>How often...</h3>
                    <h4>7. Do you drink alcohol or use mind-altering substances?</h4>
                    <h4 id="errorQ7" class="error"></h4>
                    <div class="input-group-container">
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q7" value="0" required>Never
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q7" value="1">Rarely
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q7" value="2">Monthly
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q7" value="3">Weekly
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q7" value="4">Nearly every day
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <h4>8. Have family, friends, or anyone else expressed concern over your alcohol/drug usage?</h4>
                    <h4 id="errorQ8" class="error"></h4>
                    <div class="input-group-container">
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="0" required>Never
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="1">Rarely
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="2">Sometimes
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="3">Often
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="4">Nearly every day
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <h4>9. Have you tried to control your alcohol/drug usage and had difficulty doing so?</h4>
                    <h4 id="errorQ9" class="error"></h4>
                    <div class="input-group-container">
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q9" value="0" required>Never
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q9" value="1">Rarely
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q9" value="2">Sometimes
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q9" value="3">Often
                        </span>
                        <span class="input-container">
                            <input type="radio" name="q9" value="4">Nearly every day
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <br><br>
                </div>
                <button id="submitButton" class="button" onclick="submitForm()" type="submit" >Find My
                    Therapist</button>
                <br><br>
            </form>
        </div>
        <br><br>
        <script src="../js/components/questionnaireData.js"></script>
</body>

</html>